\begin_layout Itemize
Directly revealed preference:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $x^{j}Px^{k}\iff p^{j}\cdot x^{j}>p^{j}\cdot x^{k}$
\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $x^{j}Rx^{k}\iff p^{j}\cdot x^{j}\geq p^{j}\cdot x^{k}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Indirectly revealed preference 
\begin_inset Formula $\succeq$
\end_inset

:
 transitive closure of 
